profile: Mostly Danish is a Canaidan owned interiors boutique based out of Ottawa. They specialize in sourcing and refinishing original mi-century modern, Scandinvaian and unique designer furniture. The company was founded by Zvi Gross when he immigarated to Canada and discovered his passion for woodworking and Scandinavian furniture design. Mostly Danish houses the largest warehouse of original Scandinavian and mid-century modern furniturein North America. Every piece of furniture at Mostly Danish has a story and each piece is carefully handpicked and are recognized for their simplicity, elegance and airy forms. Mostly Danish consistently offers their customers a continuously updated collection and wide selection.
